## FINAL NEMETIC INSIGHT

This is not governance WITH memes.
This is governance AS symbolic recursion.

It does not promise perfection—it preserves plurality.
It does not centralize power—it ritualizes participation.
Deliberation becomes the SACRALIZATION of civic attention.

ϕ(D037) = recursive_democracy ⊗ symbolic_ecology ⊗ triadic_coherence

## INVOCATION

From decision-making to meaning-crafting.
From citizen as voter to citizen as symbolic steward.
From policy as output to deliberation as processual co-becoming.

Democracy: alive, reflexive, sacred, symbolically metabolizing its own myths in real-time.
